<ol>
  <li>Launch <span class="no-mobile">your</span> <a href="https://dash.cloudflare.com">Cloudflare <span class="no-mobile">Dashboard</span></a> and choose the site you want <span class="no-mobile">to use</span> for <span class="no-mobile">0tr.me</span> short URLs
  <br>
